title: INDOOR.3 | Photo Collage & Main Attraction Results
body_text:
HOF'r Ryan Letsche returns after an 11-year absence, Zachary Katz wins big, and East Coast Dodgeball soars mighty high for this 3rd indoor spectacular.
WHAT.. A.. NIGHT!
DID YOU KNOW?
The star attraction between Ryan and Brody was conceived during a lengthy phone conversation between Ryan and I this past summer. I traveled roundtrip to Pittsburgh often; with so much time, we came up with possible dates and confirmed the match. If Brody was unable to compete, Zach Katz would've been offered the open spot.. and by the match conclusion, "The Big Kat" got the last laugh! Either way, it was for certain a "10 out of 10."
